{
  "stem": "3380.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had to go on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One was beating the other, you know, and running like horses around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the rabbi, was-- they gave him a goat, and he had to slaughter the goat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, they made just a-- a comedy show.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had fun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Thanks God that we were not picked up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember, I was with my brother on the attic-- hiding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we could see that they were schlepping the Jews out into the marktplatz to, you know, to make the performance.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after that, we decided-- particularly me-- I decided that I-- we have to run.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If we want to save our life, we got to get out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We also knew, at that time, that Poland has been divided-- 1/2 of Poland went to the Soviets, and 1/2 of Poland was occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to the police station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took a-- a piece of paper that I am-- a document that I am looking for a brother in Grodno.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Grodno wasn't under Russian occupation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I took my brother with me, mine oldest brother, and another brother, Leip.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was too-- he was-- he got sick with his leg, so we left him in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went back to Lask.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went to Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got into Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, that was no ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "November, it was no-- no ghetto, I mean, at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That just-- this-- this was only a preparation, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I went to Bialystok-- and I was in Bialystok until, I would say, a month or six weeks-- life was not too easy for us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had somebody that we know, a Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tannenbaum.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very kind and very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
